snippet.title: Lurkers Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Lurkers is a chaotic 2D multiplayer sandbox where you can build, battle, and survive! Fight zombies, conquer game modes like Bedwars, and unleash your creativity in a world that’s yours to shape and destroy.

Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2365750/Lurkers
Play now: https://lurkers.io
